{"tid":665903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"制衡中國擴張 美專家：應終止中國對台灣「切香腸」","createTime":"2018-05-15T11:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T04:28:22.000Z","uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e272666db04c75d6b4c45545e02db264b4ebd0e1","tid":665903,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T11:26:31.000Z","msg":"制衡中國擴張 美專家：應終止中國對台灣「切香腸」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2426110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2426110&d=cppOGrXEjPmccJsJqcfD7jCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=83095666\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2426110&h=00abab3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2426110</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國不斷對台灣進行武力恫嚇，近來更多次派出戰機、航母繞台，美國哈德遜研究所美國海權中心主任克羅普西（Seth Cropsey）在《國家評論》（nationalreview）雜誌上發表文章，呼籲美國應終止中國對台灣的持續侵犯。<br />\n<br />\n克羅普西過去曾擔任過美國國防部副次長，他強調近期中國透過實彈演習、遼寧號穿越台灣海峽、多次利用戰機繞島巡航，這些行為表面上看起來雖然是宛如「切香腸」一般的「小侵犯」，但這些行為實際上展現出台灣在第一島鏈上的關鍵角色。<br />\n<br />\n克洛普西表示，這些作為顯示了「中國的惡性意圖」，就是為了亞洲長期性衝突奠定基礎，雖然川普已經比前幾屆政府在對台政策上較一致，但克洛普西認為，這些有限的措施卻顯示出「美國外交圈對未來亞洲武力衝突的根本誤解」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">克羅普西指出，台灣是未來美中及日中競爭可能的焦點，美國須採取一貫性的亞洲政策，以藉此制衡中國的擴張主義，並且把強化台灣的安全防衛、振興美台之間的政治與外交關係置於美國戰略核心，終止中國對台灣的「切香腸做法」。</span>"},{"pid":"d4f8babc49cabf8319e9cc7fe2a9aa3e2e7d8906","tid":665903,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T11:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2390835be59e35c2842aa56d8cba9da9d3b1d25d","tid":665903,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T11:35:22.000Z","msg":"傻 識玩一定繼續比中國武力威脅先成長台獨勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13d6d2be6c7c4f45f2104fd95a23d599e10c015","tid":665903,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T12:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc1ccaed3413397dfa935a3a9746272f6a1daf1","tid":665903,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2459ad50431f759e8c8a388314c4fae09ccf2957","tid":665903,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095c2b5e385a002fb13db02f16585e6a893400e2","tid":665903,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9280acf521163bbd635b0912e5ae3401fa9970","tid":665903,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:35:42.000Z","msg":"美眾議院將啟動系列聽證會 調查中共威脅<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/667568/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/667568/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b46e28ef642ef0bcf8ec9b46cbaf657b9154969c","tid":665903,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:45:09.000Z","msg":"取消香港關係法<br />\n人仔變廢紙個時睇下中國會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f81e8b326e4e7956353ea28638b79c61a6e9235","tid":665903,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b46e28ef642ef0bcf8ec9b46cbaf657b9154969c","tid":665903,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:45:09.000Z","msg":"取消香港關係法<br />\n人仔變廢紙個時睇下中國會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}